Class FlatAccountTransferContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.beantransfer.BeanTransferContent
      • gw.sharding.FlatAccountTransferContent

  • public class FlatAccountTransferContent
extends BeanTransferContent
    This class holds a flattened representation of the beans to include when exporting an account.

      • FlatAccountTransferContent

        public FlatAccountTransferContent(Account account)
        Create a new FlatAccountTransferContent and initialize it with the set of beans to export for an account.

    • Method Detail

      • getUniqueBeans

        public java.util.Set<KeyableBean> getUniqueBeans()
        Return a unified set of the beans contained within this FlatAccountTransferContent object. Although this is not a SortedSet, the iteration order of the beans is predictable, and will be in the following sequence:
        1. EffDatedContainers
        2. EffDatedBranches
        3. EffDateds
        4. NonEffDated
        Returns:
        the set of all the beans.
